580-593年</a>，0-13岁</div><div id='fba1f5f75ba8417e9c1637b754422bb6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=580&endYear=580')\">580年</a>，当在临黄出生（出生地难确考）<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=581&endYear=590')\">581-590年</a>，随父居于临黄。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=591&endYear=591')\">591年</a>，为父守丧于临黄（本年前后其父卒）<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=592&endYear=593')\">592-593年</a>，为父守丧于临黄。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b7027174c57344e78620689a5359183b\");'><span id='b7027174c57344e78620689a5359183b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=638')\">638年</a>，58岁</div><div id='b7027174c57344e78620689a5359183b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=638')\">638年1月</a>，还乡扫墓。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.541552,"Longitude":115.312712,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN130433","Title":"馆陶","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e313f891ab7b45d4938ff629f63db396\");'><span id='e313f891ab7b45d4938ff629f63db396_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=594&endYear=602')\">594-602年</a>，14-22岁</div><div id='e313f891ab7b45d4938ff629f63db396' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=594&endYear=594')\">594年</a>，出家做道士于馆陶。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=595&endYear=602')\">595-602年</a>，道士隐居于馆陶。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e263c7584d584d86863f44fe13c15447\");'><span id='e263c7584d584d86863f44fe13c15447_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=605&endYear=617')\">605-617年</a>，25-37岁</div><div id='e263c7584d584d86863f44fe13c15447' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=605&endYear=615')\">605-615年</a>，做道士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=616&endYear=616')\">616年</a>，做道士。《道观内柏树赋并序》本年或稍前。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=617&endYear=617')\">617年8月</a>，八、九月间，出山佐郡丞元宝藏起兵。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":35.602155,"Longitude":110.718432,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN140882","Title":"河津","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a33dfcebd2c74e50a51d412fdd31b627\");'><span id='a33dfcebd2c74e50a51d412fdd31b627_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=603&endYear=603')\">603年</a>，23岁</div><div id='a33dfcebd2c74e50a51d412fdd31b627' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=603&endYear=603')\">603年</a>，去河、汾访学于王通。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.26471,"Longitude":112.610147,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN410482103","Title":"临汝","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0fd7de88d460427184519c33060f8f11\");'><span id='0fd7de88d460427184519c33060f8f11_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=604&endYear=604')\">604年</a>，24岁</div><div id='0fd7de88d460427184519c33060f8f11' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=604&endYear=604')\">604年</a>，或至崆峒山访道。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.036519,"Longitude":120.586673,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3306","Title":"绍兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"4f87874691b24e66908602a7e9c23f79\");'><span id='4f87874691b24e66908602a7e9c23f79_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=604&endYear=604')\">604年</a>，24岁</div><div id='4f87874691b24e66908602a7e9c23f79' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=604&endYear=604')\">604年</a>，游会稽，题诗山寺。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《宿沃洲山寺》<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":35.681885,"Longitude":114.557388,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN410621","Title":"浚县","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d494b4b22fdf4d079a5ec705b7ee85e6\");'><span id='d494b4b22fdf4d079a5ec705b7ee85e6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=617&endYear=617')\">617年</a>，37岁</div><div id='d494b4b22fdf4d079a5ec705b7ee85e6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=617&endYear=617')\">617年9月</a>，入李密军，掌记室。为李密作书劝降荥阳守郇王杨庆。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《为李密檄荥阳守郇王庆文》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8d4ce79c3ecc4ace824a8208fc2340f9\");'><span id='8d4ce79c3ecc4ace824a8208fc2340f9_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=619')\">618-619年</a>，38-39岁</div><div id='8d4ce79c3ecc4ace824a8208fc2340f9' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=618')\">618年11月</a>，秘书丞。，有书与徐世绩劝降。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《与徐世绩书》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=619&endYear=619')\">619年2月</a>，被窦建德俘虏，任起居舍人。为李密撰墓志铭。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《唐故邢国公李密墓志铭》<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.347436,"Longitude":108.946306,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN6101","Title":"西安","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7eae4e3540744b899ed18afc50618bb1\");'><span id='7eae4e3540744b899ed18afc50618bb1_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=618')\">618年</a>，38岁</div><div id='7eae4e3540744b899ed18afc50618bb1' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=618')\">618年10月</a>，在长安，任李密府文学参军。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"93d18d1d2f4946488683a5732e464031\");'><span id='93d18d1d2f4946488683a5732e464031_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=621&endYear=621')\">621年</a>，41岁</div><div id='93d18d1d2f4946488683a5732e464031' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=621&endYear=621')\">621年</a>，入东宫。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"20b20ad0461e40f9b0cd7d082a9f4196\");'><span id='20b20ad0461e40f9b0cd7d082a9f4196_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=622&endYear=622')\">622年</a>，42岁</div><div id='20b20ad0461e40f9b0cd7d082a9f4196' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=622&endYear=622')\">622年</a>，在长安。任太子洗马。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"fc300cbe71c2459f94151871bd99d8b3\");'><span id='fc300cbe71c2459f94151871bd99d8b3_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=623&endYear=626')\">623-626年</a>，43-46岁</div><div id='fc300cbe71c2459f94151871bd99d8b3' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=623&endYear=623')\">623年</a>，在长安。任太子洗马。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《赏旧左右议》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=624&endYear=625')\">624-625年</a>，在长安。任太子洗马。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年4月</a>，在长安。任詹事主簿。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7808c73b883b4094bbd2983eb093e46e\");'><span id='7808c73b883b4094bbd2983eb093e46e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=637')\">626-637年</a>，46-57岁</div><div id='7808c73b883b4094bbd2983eb093e46e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年9月</a>，在京任谏议大夫。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年11月</a>，迁给事中，谏诏免租赋。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《谏诏免租赋又令输纳疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=627&endYear=627')\">627年6月</a>，拜尚书右丞相。置宅东都劝善坊。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=628&endYear=628')\">628年</a>，与王圭上表请为李建成送葬。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《请陪送葬建成元吉表》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=629&endYear=629')\">629年</a>，在长安任秘书监。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=630&endYear=630')\">630年</a>，进言仁义，收聚石经。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=631&endYear=631')\">631年9月27日</a>，上所撰《群书治要》，太宗手诏答之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《群书治要序》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=632&endYear=632')\">632年4月</a>，奉敕撰《九成宫醴泉铭》<span class='label'>作品：</span>《九成宫醴泉碑铭》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年1月</a>，奉命与虞世南等改制《破阵乐》歌词。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年6月</a>，与房玄龄游戴胄卒地，数为之流涕。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年</a>，奉命作《自古诸侯王善恶录》（今已佚，仅存序）<span class='label'>作品：</span>《诸王善恶录序》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=633&endYear=633')\">633年</a>，追赠其父为定州刺史。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=634&endYear=634')\">634年</a>，得太宗赞赏孜孜辅弼之功。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=635&endYear=635')\">635年</a>，欲拜右仆射，魏征固辞之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=636&endYear=636')\">636年1月</a>，与房玄龄等上所撰五代史。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《隋书·文学传序》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=636&endYear=636')\">636年</a>，加左光禄大夫，进封郑国公。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>，上疏论君子小人。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《论君子小人疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>，上论时政第一、二、三、四疏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>，上疏论理狱与纳谏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《理狱听谏疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=637&endYear=637')\">637年</a>，于洛阳西苑积翠池宴会赋《西汉》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9e6dc09720514202a600fc2ecedec15d\");'><span id='9e6dc09720514202a600fc2ecedec15d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=643')\">638-643年</a>，58-63岁</div><div id='9e6dc09720514202a600fc2ecedec15d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=638')\">638年2月</a>，从太宗返京。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=639&endYear=639')\">639年5月</a>，上“十渐疏”<span class='label'>作品：</span>《十渐疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=639&endYear=639')\">639年</a>，参与整理御府所藏王羲之等书法作品。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=640&endYear=640')\">640年5月</a>，上所撰《类礼》二十卷。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=640&endYear=640')\">640年</a>，上疏论任臣之弊、御臣之弊。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《论御臣之疏》《论治道疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=641&endYear=641')\">641年7月</a>，谏于西域市马。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《谏遣使市马疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=641&endYear=641')\">641年10月</a>，与高士廉等撰成《文思博要》一千二百卷。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=642&endYear=642')\">642年7月</a>，卧病，太宗手诏问疾，魏征上四奏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《答太宗手诏疏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=642&endYear=642')\">642年</a>，得赐庄田于澄城县，子孙居住，称郑公庄。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=643&endYear=643')\">643年1月</a>，正月卒。临终草遗表讽谏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《遗表稿》<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.550316,"Longitude":110.253065,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN610522","Title":"潼关","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"39f26c59dca04b0db3258ed1ada3eb3a\");'><span id='39f26c59dca04b0db3258ed1ada3eb3a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=618')\">618年</a>，38岁</div><div id='39f26c59dca04b0db3258ed1ada3eb3a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=618&endYear=618')\">618年11月</a>，过潼关，有《抒怀》诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《述怀》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">述怀<span class=\"small\">（一作出关）</span>（唐·魏徵）<br />　　五言排律　押元韵</div><br /><div class='allusionNote'><span class='label'>引用典故：</span><a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=389&amp;key=%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%8c%e8%ab%be'>无二诺</a>　<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=437&amp;key=%e6%8a%95%e7%ad%86'>投笔</a>　<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=528&amp;key=%e4%be%af%e5%ac%b4'>侯嬴</a>　<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=1366&amp;key=%e8%ab%8b%e7%ba%93'>请缨</a>　<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=6034&amp;key=%e9%80%90%e9%b9%bf'>逐鹿</a>　<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=11015&amp;key=%e7%b8%b1%e6%a9%ab'>纵横</a>　</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->中原初<span class=\"small\"><a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=6034&amp;key=%e9%80%90%e9%b9%bf'>（一</a>作还）</span>逐鹿，<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=437&amp;key=%e6%8a%95%e7%ad%86'>投笔</a>事戎轩。<!--E--></p><p><!--S--><a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=11015&amp;key=%e7%b8%b1%e6%a9%ab'>纵横</a>计不就，慷慨志犹存。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->杖策谒天子，驱马出关门。<!--E--></p><p><!--S--><a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=1366&amp;key=%e8%ab%8b%e7%ba%93'>请缨</a>系南粤，凭轼下东藩。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->郁纡陟高岫，出没望平原。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->古木鸣寒鸟<span class=\"small\">（一作雁）</span>，空山啼夜猿。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->既伤千里目，还惊九折<span class=\"small\">（一作逝）</span>魂。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->岂不惮艰险，深怀国士恩。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->季布<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=389&amp;key=%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%8c%e8%ab%be'>无二诺</a>，<a target='_blank' href='Query.aspx?type=allusion&amp;id=528&amp;key=%e4%be%af%e5%ac%b4'>侯嬴</a>重一言。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->人生感意气，功名谁复论。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.631222,"Longitude":114.545808,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN1304","Title":"邯郸","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8d59febc3fdc49958ff620228846cc3b\");'><span id='8d59febc3fdc49958ff620228846cc3b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=620&endYear=620')\">620年</a>，40岁</div><div id='8d59febc3fdc49958ff620228846cc3b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=620&endYear=620')\">620年</a>，在河北任起居舍人。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":35.952793,"Longitude":114.905961,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN410527","Title":"内黄","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"3cfca765b13748f5a6e12bd8dfe88464\");'><span id='3cfca765b13748f5a6e12bd8dfe88464_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=621&endYear=621')\">621年</a>，41岁</div><div id='3cfca765b13748f5a6e12bd8dfe88464' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=621&endYear=621')\">621年</a>，本年或稍后，徙家相州内黄，后置宅于相州安阳，妻裴氏。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.713019,"Longitude":118.836327,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN370725","Title":"昌乐","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"fbe10a0ec9aa4e95ab5e29928249ce72\");'><span id='fbe10a0ec9aa4e95ab5e29928249ce72_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=622&endYear=622')\">622年</a>，42岁</div><div id='fbe10a0ec9aa4e95ab5e29928249ce72' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=622&endYear=622')\">622年12月</a>，随李建成至河北，献绥抚攻心之策，大败刘黑闼。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.38022,"Longitude":114.380351,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN130427","Title":"磁县","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a9ab49bb20304450a19036ecc1f63da2\");'><span id='a9ab49bb20304450a19036ecc1f63da2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年</a>，46岁</div><div id='a9ab49bb20304450a19036ecc1f63da2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=626&endYear=626')\">626年7月</a>，奉命出使宣慰河北，释放李建成、李元吉之党。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.778442,"Longitude":111.206832,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4112","Title":"三门峡","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e8e41d2974d84aeea88446241ec409db\");'><span id='e8e41d2974d84aeea88446241ec409db_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=638')\">638年</a>，58岁</div><div id='e8e41d2974d84aeea88446241ec409db' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=638&endYear=638')\">638年2月</a>，从太宗过陕州，观砥柱，奉命勒铭。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《砥柱山铭》<br /></div>"}],"Title":"魏征 <span class='inlineComment2'>(580-643)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：杜来梭《魏征年谱》　录入整理：亢巧霞</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 7, 115.6525525, 33.2890355, 7)\">0-37岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">范县</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">馆陶</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">河津</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">临汝</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">绍兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">馆陶</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">浚县</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(7, 12, 111.751847, 35.489329, 8)\">38-41岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">西安</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">潼关</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">浚县</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">邯郸</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">西安</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(12, 16, 113.8913165, 35.5302275, 7)\">41-46岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(12)\">内黄</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(13)\">西安</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(14)\">昌乐</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(15)\">西安</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(16, 21, 112.228501, 35.363828, 8)\">46-63岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(16)\">磁县</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(17)\">西安</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(18)\">范县</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(19)\">三门峡</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(20)\">西安</a></p>"}]}